OL,3,CJohn Lewis releases early hint of
OL,4,CChristmas ad with new campaign
OL,6,FJohn Lewis has released an early hint
OL,7,Fof its Christmas ad with a new
OL,8,Fcampaign centred on its recently
OL,9,Frevived Never Knowingly Undersold
OL,10,Fprice pledge.
OL,12,FThe "through the decades" TV advert is
OL,13,Fthe first in a three-part campaign for
OL,14,Fthe all-important retail 'golden
OL,15,Fquarter', which will culminate with
OL,16,Fthe department store's highly
OL,17,Fanticipated Christmas spot.
