OL,3,CJohn Lewis releases early hint of
OL,4,CChristmas ad with new campaign
OL,6,FThe first ad features archive footage
OL,7,Fand focuses on a single store window
OL,8,Fchanging over a century as it is
OL,9,Fdressed and redressed with products
OL,10,Fsuch as fashions of the roaring 1920s
OL,11,Fand a toaster so innovative that that
OL,12,Fit took centre stage in 1925.
OL,14,FScenes are also shown during the
OL,15,Foutbreak of the Second World War, when
OL,16,Fthe retailer's Oxford Street store `
OL,17,Fthe first John Lewis ` provided a
OL,18,Ftemporary war bunker and was hit
OL,19,Fduring the Blitz on September 18, 84
OL,20,Fyears ago.
