OL,3,CJohn Lewis releases early hint of
OL,4,CChristmas ad with new campaign
OL,6,FThe window recreates the swinging 60s
OL,7,Fand the 1980s Lycra fitness craze
OL,8,Fbefore arriving in the present day
OL,9,Fwith high-tech LED anti-ageing face
OL,10,Fmasks.
OL,12,FThe end of the ad features the Never
OL,13,FKnowingly Undersold pledge, which
OL,14,Fbegan in 1925, reinstated on the shop
OL,15,Fwindow.
OL,17,FThe ad's soundtrack, a version of Paul
OL,18,FSimon's I Know What I Know, is sung by
OL,19,FLaura Mvula, while Bafta-winning
OL,20,Factress Samantha Morton provides the
OL,21,Fvoiceover.
