OL,3,CJohn Lewis releases early hint of
OL,4,CChristmas ad with new campaign
OL,6,FJohn Lewis brought back the pledge on
OL,7,FSeptember 9 in a major U-turn after
OL,8,Fditching the commitment two years ago
OL,9,Fover concerns it was less relevant to
OL,10,Fshoppers.
OL,12,FThe retailer said sales had "increased
OL,13,Fsignificantly" since the pledge's re-
OL,14,Flaunch, and organic visits to
OL,15,Fjohnlewis.com ` or those that are
OL,16,Funpaid via search engines ` had
OL,17,Fincreased by more than 50,000 a day.
